Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:21.87,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(0,950)}genjitsu no kyoukai wo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:26.66,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,50)}hranice medzi snom a realitou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:26.66,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,50)}kaze ga sarau
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.83,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(0,0)}Alebo jednoduchšie povedané
