Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.79,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(0,500)}kagayaki dashita nichijou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:40.84,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}vyzerá, ako film, ktorý som niekde sledovala
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:40.84,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}itsuka mita eiga mitai da ne
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:45.22,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}Aj keď žijeme, ako tuláci
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:45.22,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}setsuna meguri megutte mo
