Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:53.40,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}V rieke, ktorá sa toto leto objavila
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:53.40,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}kogetta firumu no youna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.94,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}navždy stratená, ako spálený film
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.94,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}natsu no kawa ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.70,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}Vidím odraz vecí, ktorí určite prídu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.70,OPK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}utsuri de kienai yokan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:05.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur.5\fad(100,150)}Vyslobodím sa z tajomstiev, na ktoré som sa pozerala
